msgid "安信可 GPRS系列模块 FAQ"
msgstr "Ai-Thinker GPRS Series Module FAQ"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:17
#: 4cc627bd12d744298aa78dfa91051b9b
msgid "A9/A9G支持什么卡？"
msgstr "What SIM cards do A9/A9G support?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:18
#: 5a3404fde58642bf86b3148ebe3cb73a
msgid "答：A9/A9G只支持物联网卡和移动4G手机卡，暂时不支持联通，电信等手机卡"
msgstr ""
"A: A9/A9G only support IoT SIM cards and China Mobile 4G mobile SIM cards. "
"China Unicom, China Telecom, and other mobile SIM cards are not supported "
"for now."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:21
#: 2acc7fa38e4c4ba8875d5256c7056013
msgid "A9G模块定位的精度是多少？"
msgstr "What is the positioning accuracy of the A9G module?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:22
#: 7bc6effd0e3b4e77b44b9cdeaa099d40
msgid ""
"答：开阔环境下的定位精度约为4.83米（95%CEP）,在室内窗口环境下的定位精度约为"
"79.62米"
msgstr ""
"A: The positioning accuracy is about 4.83m in an open environment (95% CEP); "
"and about 79.62m in an indoor window environment."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:25
#: 67332c6e97d64e45a95240723a317c72
msgid "A9可以代替A6吗"
msgstr "Can A9 replace A6?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:26
#: 756c2f301eb941c0a5d60bb1caab0699
msgid "答：功能完全可以替代，只是脚位封装不一样"
msgstr ""
"A: Functionally, it can fully replace A6, but the pinout/package is "
"different."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:29
#: 4de4b911dd3b4f2b8634479fb0c57e2e
msgid "A9模块有对应的测试APP吗"
msgstr "Is there a corresponding test app for the A9 module?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:30
#: 9656ff5d029249088a9e86cacdf81111
msgid "https://wiki.ai-thinker.com/gprs/a9g/a9tracker"
msgstr "https://wiki.ai-thinker.com/gprs/a9g/a9tracker"

