#: 52179b8e69724e7b80e8327eae15030f
msgid "A9G，这个可以支持透传云吗"
msgstr "Does A9G support transparent transmission cloud?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:58
#: 4338cb26e19d4974a73bda3720b10396
msgid "支持透传云"
msgstr "Yes, transparent transmission cloud is supported."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:61
#: d3e53af4d49349fd808825ed0d73f36b
msgid "2G模块的传输速率大概是多少啊"
msgstr "What is the approximate transmission rate of the 2G module?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:62
#: 29cd06d9b5db4f5c95bb66bddb52cff8
msgid "下载 85.6Kbps，上传 42.8Kbps；"
msgstr "Download: 85.6Kbps; upload: 42.8Kbps."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:65
#: 15c860d56abe4ec1b769f316fb368e48
msgid "BG01-T 需要驱动吗"
msgstr "Does BG01-T require a driver?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:66
#: 64f6757d294849268f23f1c77dc4f6f2
msgid "上电就能用"
msgstr "It can be used after power-on."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:69
#: 0fad459b0f8c464dbede15a08ec00f31
msgid "A9G请问能在51单片机上用吗？ 手机端能以地图形式实时定位嘛？"
msgstr ""
"Can A9G be used with a 51 MCU? Can the mobile app display real-time "
"positioning in map form?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:70
#: f345c5ed49d54464a312a10481bd4645
msgid "只要能串口通讯就可以在51单片机上使用 ，可以定位"
msgstr ""
"As long as serial communication is possible, it can be used with a 51 MCU. "
"Positioning is supported."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:73
#: 307d599fd58e421bb1b5cf4701c092d1
msgid "A9G的二维码字符串怎么获取"
msgstr "How can I obtain the QR-code string of A9G?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:74
#: 5493ed3829774f64916e207800eb8e3d
msgid "生成二维码后生成二维码字符串"
msgstr "After generating the QR code, the QR-code string is generated."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:77
#: 22049da344b6422ca84ba65547fceab8
msgid "A9G开发板能用arduinoide吗 ？怎么编程"
msgstr ""
"Can the A9G development board be used with Arduino? How is it programmed?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:78
#: 2a68a8a44da84f9ca4555b2ed25cd875
msgid "不能。用SDK进行开发"
msgstr "No. It is developed using the SDK."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:81
#: 6f70462ab79548178843b11a762471d5
msgid "A9G模块  跑什么操作系统的？"
msgstr "What operating system does the A9G module run?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:82
#: 1e8cfedf07d342199076625cb7bc3ba1
msgid "裸机"
msgstr "Bare-metal."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:85
#: 91738f2fb8b148f5bfef278c2e96ee74
msgid "A9G 支持lua ? A9G  与A9 有些什么区别呢？支持USB么"
msgstr ""
"Does A9G support Lua? What are the differences between A9G and A9? Does it "
"support USB?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:86
#: 450abdd780774a91bfe1bbe69742dcb9
msgid "不支持lua，不支持USB ，USB是用来供电的，A9G多了一个GPS功能"
msgstr ""
"Lua is not supported. USB is not supported; USB is used for power supply. "
"A9G adds GPS functionality compared with A9."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:89
#: 0f61e55df4414d5a8effe9b592e08c6e
msgid "A9G跑的是什么协议栈"
msgstr "What protocol stack does A9G run?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:90
#: a813927105d14904b5df68e305b7ca77
msgid "GSM"
msgstr "GSM."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:92
#: b8f704d53b2c4116b0ad3d3447ca20af
msgid "A9模块在国外能使用吗？"
msgstr "Can the A9 module be used overseas?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:93
#: 70ab3bb99fe340abbb878bb3275765b5
msgid "\"亲，这个不确定，因为通信频段可能不一样，这个需要配合物联网卡使用"
msgstr ""
"It is uncertain because communication frequency bands may differ. It needs "
"to be used with an IoT SIM card."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:96
#: cf0cc07b701d426f92c389143cc87b52
msgid ""
"A9芯片回来我直接用吗？不用再下固件了吧。 那我直接发指令就可以控制是吧？通过单"
"片机串口"
msgstr ""
"After receiving the A9 chip, can I use it directly? Do I need to download "
"firmware again? Can I control it directly by sending commands through the "
"MCU serial port?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:97
#: 285b789ec13b41f9aa29ad15530f52dd
msgid "不用在下固件。是的，直接控制"
msgstr ""
"No need to download firmware again. Yes, it can be controlled directly."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:100
#: 6e3d480dbb8942378b56453ded70d7ca
msgid "\"机智云是不是不支持A9G模块了？"
msgstr "Does Gizwits no longer support the A9G module?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:101
#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:454
#: eceddc1d5b6346028034f073dcfb2ca7 c7fe8f9a42424e4fb220368aeff41b28
msgid "支持的"
msgstr "It is supported."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:104
#: 59ad4eb860234aa49f941db4ed331e39
msgid "A9G的开发板那个gps数据是从串口2读取吧？"
msgstr "Is the GPS data of the A9G development board read from UART2?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:105
#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:289
#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:364
#: 3087f0919fac459ab1d5b48eeeb2abb5 f5f159b5afe940b99f4e86de93d7998c
#: a95b0315870846c3a8f95383648807ef
msgid "是的"
msgstr "Yes."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:108
#: 74a89a3f29c0410c8670f2e702296e26
msgid "A9G开发板使用需要哪些东西？"
msgstr "What is needed to use the A9G development board?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:109
#: db74b4e1cc5a421382550440c83e53c4
msgid "开发板+CP2102.电源用电脑的USB口就可以供电,CP2102就是拿来供电还有调试的"
msgstr ""
"Development board + CP2102. The computer USB port can be used for power "
"supply. CP2102 is used for both power supply and debugging."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:112
#: 87c00423d666441d802711f35a4adaf0
msgid ""
"A9G模组的 GPRS, GPS是可以同时工作的么? 另外, 我看你们官网关于A9G模组说明里面"
"有HTTPGET方法暂不支持(下一版本支持), 那现在HTTPGET方法支持了么?"
msgstr ""
"Can GPRS and GPS of the A9G module work at the same time? Also, I saw on "
"your official website that the HTTPGET method for A9G is temporarily "
"unsupported and will be supported in the next version. Is HTTPGET supported "
"now?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:113
#: 6883a2b2509146218e02b366f11aa695
msgid "亲，是支持的哦，A9G可以get"
msgstr "Yes, it is supported. A9G can perform GET."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:116
#: ad8b51b8c124439e98e63cc2a944d1a4
msgid "请问A9模块串口能兼容5V电平吗？"
msgstr "Is the serial port of the A9 module compatible with 5V levels?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:118
#: ccb904d9b7c04894999023253357a898
msgid "不能兼容5V电平，A9供电要5V电源，电流要2A以上"
msgstr ""
"It is not compatible with 5V levels. A9 requires a 5V power supply, and the "
"current should be above 2A."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:121
#: a690558951b84facb078046f1d9ea679
msgid "A9G支持MQTT吗？"
msgstr "Does A9G support MQTT?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:123
#: e9fde4bcc928427d8025d083eca6a558
msgid "支持的，需要您二次开发哦"
msgstr "Yes, but you need to perform secondary development."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:126
#: f7f1376320ff46eea1b45709b7ebed9a
msgid "gprs如何获取模组二维码字符串"
msgstr "How does GPRS obtain the module QR-code string?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:127
#: bd61af6ae15a4d46aaadbf0de908176d
msgid "通过发送AT指令"
msgstr "By sending AT commands."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:130
#: cfe94a7e2ef74a37961e7fbf45ea5ec0
msgid "A9G开发板这个怎么开发 ？怎么实时发送温度到微信公众号？"
msgstr ""
"How do I develop with the A9G development board? How can I send temperature "
"to a WeChat official account in real time?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:131
#: f93cb392f55c417bb32db9a18e5ef370
msgid "可以进行开发，通过SDK"
msgstr "Development can be done through the SDK."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:134
#: ad61af26bc16445580175fcef024b48c
msgid ""
"请问a9模块必须与机智云软件结合起开使用吗？a9模块能与stm32f1系列开发版结合使用"
"吗？"
msgstr ""
"Must the A9 module be used together with Gizwits software? Can the A9 module "
"be used with STM32F1 series development boards?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:138
#: 0297d206b3ce4c98a6e83e1c8c3611ea
msgid ""
"GP-01，GP-02，BG01-T，BG02-T这些定位器是需要后期开发还是直接可以用？ 手机上可"
"以看定位吗"
msgstr ""
"Do GP-01, GP-02, BG01-T, and BG02-T locators require later development, or "
"can they be used directly? Can positioning be viewed on a mobile phone?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:139
#: 03fb66280334497eb32366499218c89a
msgid "直接可以使用 ，手机上看不了哦，是通过串口打印定位信息的"
msgstr ""
"They can be used directly. However, positioning cannot be viewed on a mobile "
"phone; positioning information is printed through the serial port."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:142
#: 118c43f8dfad424f96af0dfb7047011b
msgid "A9G支持MQTT的at命令吗？"
msgstr "Does A9G support MQTT AT commands?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:143
#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:324
#: a8c92d5f7f76431780f35c2dcd3b8b7a 306058c5abf34273b2c4bcac2dffd83d
msgid "支持MQTT"
msgstr "MQTT is supported."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:146
#: 618987d1e79245b3aa8f76f142ab2cdb
msgid "A9开发板支持wifi吗？"
msgstr "Does the A9 development board support Wi-Fi?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:147
#: 80e2537efb5b462b837e60aa0a82108d
msgid "A9是2G模块，不走WI-FI协议"
msgstr "A9 is a 2G module and does not use the Wi-Fi protocol."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:150
#: 1dfe281af9d04aebba42590a98618d3d
msgid "A9Tracker这个软件手机打不开啊"
msgstr "The A9Tracker software cannot be opened on the phone."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:152
#: b3e5d80c003c49cf88564cfbb014cdb3
msgid ""
"这个是软件和手机版本不兼容的原因，目前这边已经在进行更新，后续会有一个新的APP"
msgstr ""
"This is due to incompatibility between the software and the phone version. "
"We are currently updating it, and a new app will be released later."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:155
#: a61fab923b3a43febc0bfc111d513474
msgid ""
"A9G能通过一个串口读取GPS信息和进行AT控制吗？ 只能通过两个串口吗？ 两个串口分"
"别是哪两个？能二次开发吗"
msgstr ""
"Can A9G read GPS information and perform AT control through one serial port? "
"Must two serial ports be used? Which serial ports are they? Can it be "
"secondarily developed?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:156
#: 982d2bf2383e4067b4da6d854d11b082
msgid ""
"不可以哦 ，只能通过两个串口。一个是AT串口  一个是下载串口  一个是GPS串口，下"
"载串口只是做下载使用，可以二次开发"
msgstr ""
"No. It can only be done through two serial ports. One is the AT serial port, "
"one is the download serial port, and one is the GPS serial port. The "
"download serial port is only for downloading. Secondary development is "
"supported."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:159
#: 6c9e8dbb747644ea9cb0e9eb92213ffb
msgid "A9开发板供电可以极限是5.5V吗？5.28会有问题吗"
msgstr ""
"Is the maximum power supply limit of the A9 development board 5.5V? Will "
"5.28V cause problems?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:160
#: cbbfcd917d9f4260974a2c8a978a17c4
msgid "5V。应该会有哦，因为模块供电范围是3.8V-4.2V，USB是做了降压电路处理"
msgstr ""
"5V. It may cause problems because the module power supply range is 3.8V to "
"4.2V. The USB port has a step-down circuit."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:163
#: 2eeaba2167054afa93eb10b1af50d3da
msgid "A9G开发板可以刷NodeMCU 吗"
msgstr "Can the A9G development board flash NodeMCU?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:165
#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:252
#: 1f24d1c0dfde4f298471253d843dfc21 d0355d39509146778372845cfcceb81e
msgid "不行哦"
msgstr "No."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:168
#: 8dcc8fe15e274ec799170a1541c44b7c
msgid "A9G模块能和3.3v的单片机直接相连吗？"
msgstr "Can the A9G module be directly connected to a 3.3V MCU?"

