#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:594
#: d4f0af15bce44176b587f33c9417afae
msgid "A9G连接机智云出现ERROR:50该如何处理？"
msgstr "How to handle ERROR:50 when A9G connects to Gizwits?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:595
#: 587ede0ef37747c6acfe67dfa7793d33
msgid ""
"先发送AT+CGATT=0分离上一次的附着，在发送AT+CGATT=1，AT+CGDCONT=1,\"IP\","
"\"CMNET\"，AT+CGACT=1,1三条指令重新入网"
msgstr ""
"First send AT+CGATT=0 to detach from the previous attachment, then send AT"
"+CGATT=1, AT+CGDCONT=1,\"IP\",\"CMNET\", and AT+CGACT=1,1 to re-register on "
"the network."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:598
#: 4ca66b88c7da45a383747ec4c12469cb
msgid "A9G模块为何获取不到定位数据？"
msgstr "Why can’t the A9G module obtain positioning data?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:599
#: 5f62bb746752495381bb8a12596968d0
msgid "单模组情况，考虑匹配的天线有问题。"
msgstr ""
"For a standalone module, consider whether there is a problem with the "
"matched antenna."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:602
#: 250ac6ce1e25461ab92af771eefd8173
msgid "A9G断电后重新上电无法联网导致机智云失败，该如何解决"
msgstr ""
"How to solve Gizwits failure caused by A9G being unable to reconnect to the "
"network after power-off and power-on?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:603
#: d29315d304714923b6f0892c62469fc9
msgid ""
"先发送AT+CGATT=0分离上一次的网络附着，后面重新发送AT+CGATT=1，AT+CGDCONT=1,"
"\"IP\",\"CMNET\"，AT+CGACT=1,1重新附着网络即可"
msgstr ""
"First send AT+CGATT=0 to detach from the previous network attachment, then "
"send AT+CGATT=1, AT+CGDCONT=1,\"IP\",\"CMNET\", and AT+CGACT=1,1 to attach "
"to the network again."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:606
#: b6055c455ece4de19bd71949d81a1fdb
msgid "A9G打电话的时候接话筒声音小该如何解决"
msgstr "How to solve low microphone/receiver volume during calls on A9G?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:607
#: 7339885cb6944285a6a5aee101e8371f
msgid "尝试发送AT+CRSL=15设置一下通话音量的等级。"
msgstr "Try sending AT+CRSL=15 to set the call volume level."

