msgstr ""
"If only the networking function is abnormal, the SIM card data may have been "
"used up. Please confirm with the carrier service staff."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:618
#: 38ded17d7f7441ad8200e9a43d97106a
msgid "A9G实现不了你们公众号的定位功能怎么办？"
msgstr ""
"What should I do if A9G can no longer implement the positioning function "
"from your WeChat official account?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:619
#: b208315261a94ce7b7ab65064a2e1f41
msgid ""
"该功能已没有维护了，因此若是要实现定位功能，建议通过MQTT协议连接阿里的定位功"
"能。详情参考我们EC-01G连接阿里云地图实现定位的文档。"
msgstr ""
"This function is no longer maintained. Therefore, if you need positioning "
"functionality, it is recommended to connect to Alibaba's positioning "
"function through the MQTT protocol. For details, refer to our document on "
"EC-01G connecting to Alibaba Cloud Map for positioning."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPRS/index.rst:622
